  <summary date="2017-10-12T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Title IX Protection Act

This bill amends the Department of Education Organization Act to require recipients of federal financial assistance to comply with specified procedural requirements when responding to sexual harassment and sexual violence to&#160;prevent and effectively respond to sexual discrimination as required by title IX of the Education Amendments of 1972.</summary>
